---
// About 页（F023 转化核心）：站长可信故事 + 作者信任条（F014）+ 联系表单（F015）。
// 事实来自规格：博士学位；北海本地人；英语流利；曾在欧美生活 4 年。
// 保持每页 SEO 唯一（F004）：与首页不同的 title/description，og:image 走默认回退。
// 正文纯英文（双语政策），仅地名保留中英对照（Beihai 北海）。
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import AuthorTrust from '../components/AuthorTrust.astro';
import ContactForm from '../components/ContactForm.astro';
import PhotoPlaceholder from '../components/PhotoPlaceholder.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About — No Visa China"
  description="Who is behind No Visa China and how these guides are researched and verified on the ground."
>
  <main>
    <article class="about">
      <h1>About</h1>
      <AuthorTrust />

      <div class="portrait">
        <PhotoPlaceholder caption="Portrait of the author" />
      </div>

      <p class="lead">
        I grew up here, and I want travellers to see the real thing — not a
        rushed tour-bus version of it.
      </p>
      <p>
        I hold a PhD and I am a Beihai 北海 local. English is a language I speak
        fluently, and I spent four years living in Europe and the United States,
        so I know what it feels like to land somewhere new and need honest,
        practical directions rather than marketing copy.
      </p>
      <p>
        Every guide here is researched and checked on the ground, then written
        for independent travellers who plan their own trips. If something has
        changed since I last visited, I want to hear about it.
      </p>
    </article>

    <ContactForm />
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* 可读行宽：正文限 640px（比 main 的 1100px 窄），移动端 max-width:100% 不溢出。 */
  .about {
    max-width: 640px;
  }
  .about h1 {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .portrait {
    max-width: 320px;
    margin: 24px 0 32px;
  }
  .lead {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-top: 24px;
  }
  .about p + p {
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
</style>
